&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;i&gt;Some phyllotaxis-like spirals (&lt;a href="https://www.desmos.com/calculator/risuha09iw"&gt;graph here&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To create these, take the basic equation mentioned with this definition for the two sequences&lt;br /&gt;
