&lt;span style="font-size: large;"&gt;Quadratic number spirals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
I first saw quadratic number spirals at &lt;a href="http://numberspiral.com/"&gt;numberspiral.com&lt;/a&gt;. A quadratic spiral also fits into the basic spiral form mentioned above (graph here)/&lt;br /&gt;
